yee={"arguments": "{\n  \"Story\": \"Gathering your courage, you step forward, ready to embrace the challenge. You can tell that Tina looks surprised but she quickly masks it with a smirk. As the other kids circle around, you take a deep breath and start swinging your Yo-Yo. The game is on. Terrible Tina is a formidable opponent, her yo-yo crisp and movements deft. However, you've been practicing for weeks, and your fancy 'Walk the Dog' trick earns you awed gasps from the onlookers. In the end, it's clear who the victor is \u2013 you! \\n\\nTina skulks away, plotting her revenge surely, but today, you've earned your moment in the sun. Some kids even clap! With mixed feelings of elation and wariness, you realize the recess has only just begun and there's much more to be done.\",\n  \"Time\": 15,\n  \"Friends\": {\n    \"Acquaintances\": {\n      \"count\": 3,\n      \"info\": \"The three kids who clapped might become friends.\"\n    },\n    \"Friends\": {\n      \"count\": 0,\n      \"info\": \"\"\n    },\n    \"Best Friend\": {\n      \"count\": 0,\n      \"info\": \"\"\n    },\n    \"Enemies\": {\n      \"count\": 1,\n      \"info\": \"Terrible Tina\"\n    },\n    \"Arch Nemesis\": {\n      \"count\": 0,\n      \"info\": \"\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"Items\": [\"Ouija Board\", \"Rubber Duck\", \"Yo-Yo\", \"Pack of Colored Pencils\", \"Hardcover Fantasy Book\"]\n}"}